(1829, 174, 'about', 'Message Broadcast operates an interactive multi-channel message delivery network supporting automated inbound and outbound Voice, Interactive Voice Response (IVR), Mobile/Text, Email and Broadband communications.'),
(1830, 174, 'project', 'Message Broadcast selected SETA International to provide a dedicated team of software developers to assist with their new web-based ERP system build-out. To meet Message Broadcast''s time-to-market goals, the follow-the-sun development model was implemented utilizing SETA engineers in Vietnam, the United States and Ireland.'),
(1831, 174, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>ERP Engineering expertise</li>\r\n	<li>Streamlined project management over multiple sites</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering expertise with Coldfusion, Flash, MySQL</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced use of Javascript, jQuery and Raphael library to draw objects</li>\r\n	<li>Voice processing knowledge</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1832, 174, 'success', 'SETA International''s staffing augmentation services enabled Message Broadcast to launch their ERP system on schedule, with lower development costs than if they had utilized their own teams.'),
(1839, 176, 'url', ' http://puredrop.co.uk'),
(1840, 176, 'about', 'Puredrop helps businesses with all their IT needs, from consultancy and interim management to product and software development'),
(1841, 176, 'project', 'Puredrop chose SETA international to assist them in developing a tablet application for recording and storing building inspection data during monitoring visits for compliance with Health and Safety legislation. The tablet application replaced paper forms and allowed for easy synchronization via web service. The tablet application was required to be able to communicate both wired and wirelessly with a server application.'),
(1842, 176, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Tablet application development</li>\r\n	<li>Best practice advice on tablet UI</li>\r\n	<li>Synchronization function</li>\r\n	<li>Application installation function</li>\r\n	<li>Support during user acceptance testing</li>\r\n	<li>All source code</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1843, 176, 'success', 'SETA International''s tablet development services enabled PureDrop to successfully launch their tablet application and helped reduce the cost of physical documents throughout their organization.'),
(1850, 175, 'url', ''),
(1851, 175, 'about', ''),
(1852, 175, 'project', 'The State of Oregon selected SETA International to develop and build an iPAD application to enable their census takers to easily collect data from Oregon households from the U.S.2010 Census. The data could then quickly and accurately be synchronized with the census database'),
(1853, 175, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Project discovery to determine how the iPad application will connect and interact with Oregon''s secured backend application</li>\r\n	<li>Secured the data stream between the iOS application and the backend application</li>\r\n	<li>Streamlined project management over multiple sites</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering expertise with iOS, SQL, PHP, etc</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1854, 175, 'success', 'SETA International''s iOS development services enabled the State of Oregon to effectively deploy the iPad application to all of their census takers to take household data for the U.S. census.'),
(1861, 173, 'url', ''),
(1862, 173, 'about', 'Mobcast is a publisher and developer of original video games for mobile phones. Established in 2004, they operate six paid game sites and own 100+ mobile games.'),
(1863, 173, 'project', 'Facing increasing demand for online games in the Japanese market, Mobcast needed to scale up their production while maintaining their quality standards.\r\nThey chose SETA International to provide a dedicated offsite team of experienced mobile gaming developers and quality assurance engineers to complement their on-site gaming development team.\r\nOur team completed end-to-end development of the Eleon Blade/Knight online role-playing game that has now been released on all Japanese mobile platforms.'),
(1864, 173, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>ignificant experience with mobile technologies including the Android device platform and Flash Lite</li>\r\n	<li>xpertise in mobile enablement of web games</li>\r\n	<li>dvanced features (Globalization/ Localization)</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1865, 173, 'success', 'Our efficient game development and design allowed Mobcast to bring the game to market faster and at a lower cost than if they had developed internally.\r\nSETAs professionalism and execution skills have enabled Mobcast Japan to leverage SETAs engineering resources to assist us with our game application roadmap. Their flexibility and scalability ensure that the right resources are available to meet our needs. --Yabu Koki, CEO/President (Mobcast Group Japan)'),
(1872, 172, 'url', ' http://www.bestfashionfr'),
(1873, 172, 'about', 'Best Fashion Friend is a smartphone app that gives users gives users instant access to a handpicked group of friends for comment on style dilemmas. A user snaps a photo of the chosen apparel, creates fashion looks using items they own or are considering for purchase, and then shares the looks with their BFFs for real-time advice and comment. Users can even post their looks to Facebook as status updates.'),
(1874, 172, 'project', 'This mobile application development project included design, development, optimization, and deployment of BFF systems, including a centralized web application and iPhone and Android Application. It was specifically designed to integrate seamlessly with Facebook to facilitate user adoption. The features of this mobile app include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Camera function to take a picture and save it in your virtual closet</li>\r\n	<li>BFF function allows the user to create a look in the mirror and easily share it will your BFFs.</li>\r\n	<li>Size, rotate, and layer items with the Closet Function.</li>\r\n	<li>Tidy up your wardrobe with the Toss function</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1875, 172, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Facebook Integration</li>\r\n	<li>Graphical Design/ Wireframes (Adobe Photoshop, Microsoft Visio)</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Technologies (iPhone, Android)</li>\r\n	<li>Web Technologies (Symphony Framework, Flash)</li>\r\n	<li>Database Technologies (SQLite, MySQL)</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced features (Data Synchronization between Mobile Application and Web services, Web Balancing, Cloud Server Setup</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1876, 172, 'success', 'Our competitively priced software development services enabled Manacor to get their application to market faster while lowering their overall development costs.\r\n"My sincere thanks to you and your team for the hard work to get app out in the market place. We feel confident that the marketplace will find it interesting, will adopt it, and will use it." --Ricardo Cuervo, Manacor Group'),
(1883, 171, 'url', ' http://www.osirisshoes.c'),
(1884, 171, 'about', 'Osiris is a leading provider of apparel and shoes designed for skateboarding, surfing, motocross and casual wear. They sponsor a variety of athletes including skate, BMX, FMX, and MTB.'),
(1885, 171, 'project', 'Osiris wanted to broaden their direct marketing channel to include paths for smartphone users to discover their products and overall brand. They chose SETA International to design 12 QR codes and a mobile site with an iPhone application look and feel that promoted their products and showcased their athletes.\r\nSETA International also developed an on-line analytics dashboard that provided Osiris with instant access to crucial customer data. Osiris was able to track campaign saturation and geographical relevance in real time.'),
(1886, 171, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Application Development</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Enablement</li>\r\n	<li>Analytics Dashboard to display on-demand analytics for Osiris''s mobile and campaign</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering expertise with PHP, iOS and Android technologies</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1887, 171, 'success', 'Working with SETA International enabled Osiris to create a new marketing channel featuring QR code integration with mobile applications. SETA was able to speed Osiris''s time to market while lowering their overall development cost.'),
(1894, 170, 'url', 'http://www.pan'),
(1895, 170, 'about', 'Panavision is one of Hollywood''s signature brands when it comes to the highest quality in film image acquisition.'),
(1896, 170, 'project', 'Panavision chose SETA International to complete a mobile application development project that entitled developing their first ever iPhone application, Panascout. Panascout enables the iPhone to simulate a cinematographer''s viewpoint from a professional cinema camera and captures the metadata needed to plan full days of shooting. It has an extensive features list.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PANAFRAME (2.40, 1.85, 1.78, 1.33)</li>\r\n	<li>Date / Time</li>\r\n	<li>Email</li>\r\n	<li>iPhone Library Save</li>\r\n	<li>GPS coordinates</li>\r\n	<li>Compass direction (3GS only)</li>\r\n	<li>Sunrise/Sunset</li>\r\n	<li>Upload to Final Cut Server, MobileMe, SmugMug</li>\r\n	<li>Video (3GS only)</li>\r\n	<li>Album/Roll Save</li>\r\n	<li>Voice Notes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur experienced engineering teams enabled Panavision to get Panascout to market quickly and on budget. We also developed the supporting website http://www.panascout.com.'),
(1897, 170, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Graphical Design/ Wireframes (Adobe Photoshop, OrmiFlare)</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Technologies (Objective C, Iphone SDK)</li>\r\n	<li>Database Technologies (SQLite)</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Technologies (GPS Intergration, On-Demand data Streaming)</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1898, 170, 'success', 'On day 2 of Panascout''s release, it was one of the top 200 most downloaded applications on iTunes.'),
(1905, 169, 'url', 'https://www.aacargo.'),
(1906, 169, 'about', 'American Airlines Cargo, a division of American Airlines, Inc., provides more than 100 million pounds of weekly cargo lift capacity to major cities in the United States, Europe, Canada, Mexico, the Caribbean, Latin America and Asia. For almost 80 years, they have relentlessly innovated cargo technology and expanded their global network.'),
(1907, 169, 'project', 'American Airlines Cargo selected SETA International to develop a micro-site, aacargo.com. In addition to providing all the information needed to ship cargo, the site allows users to check rates, book shipments and track packages. We leveraged our strategic partnership with Rhythm Interactive, who produced the graphic assets for the project.'),
(1908, 169, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Web Application Development built in PHP</li>\r\n	<li>Content Management System</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Enablement</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering expertise with PHP and WordPress technologies</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1909, 169, 'success', 'By working with SETA International, American Airlines Cargo was able to launch a dynamic, interactive micro web site faster and with lower development costs than if they had developed it internally.'),
(1916, 159, 'url', ' http://lucid.la'),
(1917, 159, 'about', 'Lucid is a spirited, creative group with big ideas and the audacity to bring them to life. Working with clients like Mattel, Panasonic, Fox and Red Bull, Lucid helps build provocative brands for today''s fast paced, digital engagement landscape.'),
(1918, 159, 'project', 'As a full-service agency, Lucid provides an end-to-end solution to all of their clients. Lucid chose SETA International as their sole technology partner to assist them with all of their back-end technology needs.\r\nSETA developed a WYSIWYG content management system (CMS) with an extensive feature list that enables Lucid update content, information, and assets seamlessly and effortlessly.'),
(1919, 159, 'technical_competency', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Web Technologies (PHP, ASP.NET, ROR, Flash, JQuery)</li>\r\n	<li>Database Technologies (MySQL, MS SQL)</li>\r\n	<li>CMS Technologies (Drupal, WordPress, Joomla)</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Techonology (iPhone, Droid)</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1920, 159, 'success', 'By working with SETA International, Lucid was able to bring their new CMS online faster and with lower development costs than if they had developed internally.'),
