(6844, 417, 'description', 'James Dolan is the Marketing Director at SETA International, specializing in providing International - Multilingual search engine marketing management services for global advertising agencies, search engine marketing and Fortune 1000 firms. Since 2001, James has been a leading expert in the search engine marketing and optimization community with a passion for staying current with this ever changing industry and cutting edge strategies.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBefore working at SETA, James worked as Director of Search Marketing at the agency level providing optimization strategies to e-commerce, publishing and corporate internet properties. He has worked on SEO campaigns from a broad base of clients in a number of industries including: technology services, education, healthcare, hospitality and retail.'),
