(6832, 71, 'description', 'As a trusted advisor and strategist for SETA International, Mr. McEvoy has served in a variety of advisory roles and has been a primary contributor to the companys growth and expansion into Japan and Europe. Mr. McEvoy provides both strategic direction and tactical planning in the areas of product delivery, services, sales, marketing and business planning. An experienced operations manager, Mr. McEvoy has also held senior and executive positions at a number of Fortune 100 companies across multiple disciplines such as strategic outsourcing, channel support, services and product development.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMr. McEvoy holds a BSc. in Software Engineering and an MBA in Global Business Strategy.'),
