(7068, 487, 'description', '<p><strong>U.H.P. Tire L.L.C.</strong> is a global tire supplier and distribution company with offices located in Santa Monica, U.S.A., Dubai, U.A.E, Mexico D.F., Mexico, and sourcing offices in Tokyo, Japan, and Qingdao, China.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>U.H.P. Tire L.L.C.</strong> effectively utilizes its sourcing offices across Asia and the Middle East and its warehouse facility in Dubai, U.A.E., to offer a complete range of tires, including Off-The-Road, Truck and Bus, Passenger, Agricultural, and Industrial tires. <strong>U.H.P. Tire L.L.C.</strong> understands the value of quality and service in this industry, and strict guidelines are followed by its internal logistics department to ensure that all tires are ordered and delivered on time to the customer. Furthermore, <strong>U.H.P. Tire L.L.C.</strong> only supplies brand new tires manufactured according to the requirements and specifications of its customers with complete international quality certifications and warranty provided by the manufacturer. <strong><br /></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SETA was selected by UHP Tires Global to design and develop their new website which also included the development of a new order management system. SETA worked very closely with the UHP Global team to capture all of their requirements and expectations which resulted to a successful project and over exceeded their expectations.</p>'),
