(7159, 491, 'description', '<p>Lexues Inc. was founded in 1998, during the booming dot-com bubble days, when we developed and began offering free of charge Japans first full-fledged Web-based groupware, Team Gear. Even today, this service continues to be frequently covered by the mass media. Immediately after Team Gear came out, OEM arrangements were set up to provide the service for numerous portal sites and universities, and in subsequent years the groupware market has thrived. As is evident from all this, this service has become a symbol of our foresight and efficiency in creating communication services.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SETA has entered into a formal agreement with Lexues as one of their strategic technology partners to assist with their internal and external software development needs. SETA provides Lexues with high quality software developers whom work closely with their internal organization to maximize their efficiency and productivity across the globe. Once Lexues integrated SETA''s hybrid development model, they were able to quickly achieve efficiency across their organization while reducing overall operational cost and maximizing ROI.</p>'),
