(8230, 496, 'description', '<p>  JISQ15001 </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SETA was selected by Attic Arcade to design and develop their new website from the ground up. From project discovery to deployment, SETA worked very closely with the AA team during the entire project lifecycle. This enabled SETA to capture all of Attic''s requirements and expectations which resulted to a successful project and over exceeded their expectations.</p>'),
