(8668, 413, '_amt_description', 'As a trusted advisor for SETA-International, Mr. Watanabe has served in a variety of advisory roles and has been instrumental in assisting the principals with the company foundation as well as its growth in North America and Japan. Mr. Watanabe provides strategic direction in the areas of business development, corporate strategy and strategic marketing as a results-oriented technology leader with over 10+ years of experience in Information Technology.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMr. Watanabe is proficient in business-economic models, strategic outsourcing, offshore operations and strategic business planning. He also has worldwide experience leading offshore operations for a number of Fortune 100 companies in Ireland, India, China and Vietnam.\r\n'),
(8702, 413, 'description', 'As a trusted advisor for SETA-International, Mr. Watanabe has served in a variety of advisory roles and has been instrumental in assisting the principals with the company foundation as well as its growth in North America and Japan. Mr. Watanabe provides strategic direction in the areas of business development, corporate strategy and strategic marketing as a results-oriented technology leader with over 10+ years of experience in Information Technology.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMr. Watanabe is proficient in business-economic models, strategic outsourcing, offshore operations and strategic business planning. He also has worldwide experience leading offshore operations for a number of Fortune 100 companies in Ireland, India, China and Vietnam.\r\n'),
(8680, 247, 'description', '<p>mUrgent provides a wide variety of marketing solutions for companies of all sizes in diverse and dynamic industries such as restaurants, retails, and franchises - with the experience and capabilities to create sophisticated campaigns for major national corporations as well as options for growing businesses. As a foremost leader in local store marketing solutions in a highly competitive industry, mUrgent understands the value of leading edge technology, eliminating outdated and high maintenance systems, powerful web application development, and ensuring ROI for both the organization and its customers  thats why SETA-International is mUrgents best investment choice for systems consultation and end to end web application development.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>At SETA were excited to play an instrumental role in providing mUrgent quality consultations about their systems, how to minimize cost and maximize efficiency through new and scalable options  building mUrgent the latest front end to back end web development solution and providing on-going systems maintenance and administration. Its our job to give them the best tools  so they can stay focus on being the best marketing tools for their customers.</p>'),
(8686, 153, '_amt_description', 'VisionCourse Media is the ultimate resource for all your ecommerce needs. Platforms we specialize in are Bigcommerce, Magento, ProStores, eBay, 3Dcart, and WordPress, as well as many others. - See more at: http://www.visioncourse.com/#sthash.frSbcpOR.dpuf<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSETA has entered into a formal agreement with Vision Course to assist with their product development roadmap that includes the augmentation of their internal staff by integrating our industry leading hybrid dedicated team model into their organization.'),
(8693, 153, 'description', '<p>VisionCourse Media is the ultimate resource for all your ecommerce needs. Platforms we specialize in are Bigcommerce, Magento, ProStores, eBay, 3Dcart, and WordPress, as well as many others. - See more at: <a href="http://www.visioncourse.com/#sthash.frSbcpOR.dpuf" target="_blank">http://www.visioncourse.com/#sthash.frSbcpOR.dpuf</a></p><p>SETA has entered into a formal agreement with Vision Course to assist with their product development roadmap that includes the augmentation of their internal staff by integrating our industry leading hybrid dedicated team model into their organization.</p>'),
