(8740, 659, 'description', 'Arron Hunt is the Head of Innovation & Creative at SETA International (North America).  Arron has been making tracks in the design industry for numerous years and his core mission is to focus on building innovative and ground breaking products at SETA.  Arron eats, sleeps, and breaths interactive design and has a strong track record of delivering successful projects taking our client''s ideas from concept to reality.'),
