(310, 2, '2013-02-05 10:07:20', '2013-02-05 10:07:20', '<p>AppFactory, is a new company established by SK Planet in 2012, a globally recognized and respected leader in innovative mobile services. AppFactorys mission is to transform great ideas into compelling mobile apps for the global market. SK Planet was created by SK Telecom in November 2011 with the purpose of focusing on global businesses, including new media and digital content.</p><p>SETA was selected by AppFactory to help augment their internal product development team and assist with their product roadmap for 2013.</p>', 'AppFactory', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'appfactory', '', '', '2013-10-29 04:20:40', '2013-10-29 04:20:40', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=310', 21, 'news', '', 0),
(311, 2, '2013-01-05 10:08:41', '2013-01-05 10:08:41', '<p>In 1992, the HEAROS brand of earplugs was launched to help customers reduce noise, protect hearing and defend against water damage to the ear. Eighteen years later, HEAROS earplugs have transformed into a worldwide enterprise with distribution in over 50,000 retail stores.</p><p>DAP World selected SETA to help lead and drive their technology strategy and initiatives which includes the development of a number of web and mobile properties to help compliment and market their ever growing products worldwide.</p>', 'DAP World', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dap-world', '', '', '2013-10-29 04:05:01', '2013-10-29 04:05:01', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=311', 2, 'news', '', 0),
(312, 2, '2012-12-05 10:09:46', '2012-12-05 10:09:46', '<p>Yourkidvid (A Tuttare Company) will revolutionize how consumers will develop video scrapbooks through web and mobile.</p><p>SETA was selected by Tuttare Corporation to build a new social media web and mobile application that will include rich features such as video editing, video sharing, social media integration and much more.</p><p>Stay tuned for the official release of the application scheduled for later this year.</p>', 'yourkidvid.com', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'yourkidvid-com', '', '', '2013-10-29 04:20:21', '2013-10-29 04:20:21', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=312', 20, 'news', '', 0),
(313, 2, '2012-11-05 10:10:53', '2012-11-05 10:10:53', '<p>As a global leader in cloud security, Trend Micro develops Internet content security and threat management solutions that make the world safe for businesses and consumers to exchange digital information. With more than 20 years of experience, Trend Micro is recognized as the market leader in server security for delivering top-ranked client, server, and cloud-based security solutions that stop threats faster and protect data in physical, virtualized, and cloud environments.</p><p>SETA was selected by Trend Micro to build an internal .NET application that included software development, quality assurance and on-going maintenance and support of the application.</p>', 'Trend Micro', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trend-micro', '', '', '2013-10-29 04:06:27', '2013-10-29 04:06:27', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=313', 5, 'news', '', 0),
(314, 2, '2012-10-05 10:11:45', '2012-10-05 10:11:45', '<p>Somo was set up to help businesses make sense of mobile. The team has a wealth of internet, advertising and mobile expertise and experience. We are independent of any planning or buying agencies, ensuring we recommend the most appropriate media for our clients. We have a team of skilled designers who create innovative products to run across the range of handsets and operating systems.</p><p>SETA was selected by Somo Global as their strategic technology partner assisting them with system architecture, software development, quality assurance and on-going maintenance and support for all of their technical service needs.</p>', 'Somo Global', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'somo-global', '', '', '2013-10-29 04:19:56', '2013-10-29 04:19:56', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=314', 19, 'news', '', 0),
(315, 2, '2012-10-05 10:12:23', '2012-10-05 10:12:23', '<p>SETA was selected by MedTalk to build an end-to-end mobile messaging platform that will serve as the platform of choice for mobile messaging in the medical industry. This platform and solution will address the present inefficient communication amongst doctors and their on-call staff with regards to delay and lag time in the communication response times. MedTalk was established by two doctors whom had an innovated idea but needed a strong technical partner to help architect and develop their business vision into a tangible platform.</p>', 'MedTalk', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'medtalk', '', '', '2013-10-29 04:19:37', '2013-10-29 04:19:37', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=315', 18, 'news', '', 0),
(316, 2, '2012-09-05 10:13:04', '2012-09-05 10:13:04', '<p>The Golden Spoon story began in 1981 as an outgrowth of "Yogurt and Things," a health food store in Tustin, California acquired by Golden Spoon founder Jeff Barnes in 1980. Within a year, Barnes opted to leave the "Things" behind and focus solely on frozen yogurt with the goal of creating a more broadly appealing, and healthier frozen dessert than anything available on the market at the time. Barnes succeeded and sales at his original Tustin store more than doubled within those first few years. In 1983, the Golden Spoon brand name was born.</p><p>SETA was chosen by Golden Spoon to build a new mobile application that will include robust features and functionality not yet available to the public. Golden Spoon and SETA plans on releasing both the iOS and Android version of the mobile application in October of 2012.</p>', 'Golden Spoon', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'golden-spoon', '', '', '2013-10-30 03:43:21', '2013-10-30 03:43:21', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=316', 17, 'news', '', 0),
(317, 2, '2012-07-05 10:14:59', '2012-07-05 10:14:59', '<p>mUrgent provides a wide variety of marketing solutions for companies of all sizes in diverse and dynamic industries such as restaurants, retails, and franchises - with the experience and capabilities to create sophisticated campaigns for major national corporations as well as options for growing businesses.</p><p>As a foremost leader in local store marketing solutions in a highly competitive industry, mUrgent understands the value of leading edge technology, eliminating outdated and high maintenance systems, powerful web application development, and ensuring ROI for both the organization and its customers  thats why SETA-International is mUrgents best investment choice for systems consultation and end to end web application development.</p><p>At SETA were excited to play an instrumental role in providing mUrgent quality consultations about their systems, how to minimize cost and maximize efficiency through new and scalable options  building mUrgent the latest front end to back end web development solution and providing on-going systems maintenance and administration. Its our job to give them the best tools  so they can stay focus on being the best marketing tools for their customers.</p>', 'mUrgent', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'murgent', '', '', '2013-11-14 11:52:29', '2013-11-14 11:52:29', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=317', 16, 'news', '', 0),
(318, 2, '2012-06-05 10:15:50', '2012-06-05 10:15:50', '<p>Vision Course has selected SETA International to assist with the development of a new cloud based application for one of their key customers.</p><p>SETA''s sales and support teams had worked extensively with Vision Course to help identify and drive the value proposition and overall solution which ultimately enabled SETA to win this opportunity.</p><p>SETA will provide technical consulting and application development services to assist Vision Course with a development of a new cloud based CRM system.</p>', 'Vision Course', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vision-course', '', '', '2013-10-29 04:18:05', '2013-10-29 04:18:05', '', 0, '/?post_type=news&#038;p=318', 15, 'news', '', 0),
