(533, 1, '2013-09-30 09:21:52', '2013-09-30 09:21:52', '<div id="offshore1"><h1>Outsourcing is More <br /> Than Cutting Cost</h1><div id="contact-right">1-888-852-8374 <br /> <a href="mailto:info@seta-international.com">info@seta-international.com</a></div><p><a id="download_data_sheet" href="http://www.seta-international.com/files/Seta_international_datasheet.pdf" target="_blank">download</a></p><div id="text-content">At SETA International, we know how difficult it is to find the right offshore or outsourced developers and engineers for your project. Outsourcing your development needs is about more than just lowering costs. You need assurances that the talent level aligns with your business objectives, your Intellectual Property is protected, and communication is fluid. You want a partner that understands your needs and adds value to your business. Its about cutting cost without sacrificing the standards, quality, security, flexibility and reliability of a local company. For more info, call us at 1-888-852-8374.</div><p><a id="dedicated-submit" href="#fancybox-contact"></a></p></div><div id="offshore2"><h1>Key Differentiators:</h1><ul id="offshore2-content"><li><span><b>Hybrid Onshore-Offshore model:</b> Streamlined process using onshore management &amp; expertise with talented offshore resources.</span><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><span><b>Competitive Rates:</b> Our globally competitive rates are typically 33% lower than local rates.</span><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><span><b>Security:</b> We implement U.S. standard security protocols to ensure your IP is fully protected.</span><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><span><b>Global Talent:</b> 70% SETAs Offshore Development engineers have MS degrees.</span><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><span><b>Delivery:</b> 96% of projects are completed on time, 100% are completed on budget.</span><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><span><b>Satisfaction:</b> 85% of our clients come back to work with us again.</span><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><span><b>Stability:</b> Low turnover rates 