 <br /> Blackberry <br /> Windows Mobile<p><a class="mobile-dev" title="MOBILE APPLICATIONS DEVELOPMENT" href="/mobile-applications-development.html">more...</a></p></td><td>iPad <br /> Android <br /> Blackberry <br /> <p><a class="tablet-dev" title="TABLET APPLICATIONS DEVELOPMENT" href="/tablet-applications-development.html">more...</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class="overview-different-chart clearfix"><div class="global-chart"><div class="group"><div class="overview-chart" data-chart-value="70, 30" data-chart-label="70">70</div></div><p class="overview-chart-description"><b>Global Talent:</b>70% of Setas <br /> Offshore Development engineers <br /> have MS degrees.</p></div><div class="delivery-chart"><div class="group"><div class="overview-chart" data-chart-value="96, 4" data-chart-label="96">96</div><div class="overview-chart" data-chart-value="100, 0" data-chart-label="100">100</div></div><p class="overview-chart-description"><b>Delivery:</b>96% of projects are completed on time, <br /> 100% are completed on budget.</p></div><div class="satisfaction-chart"><div class="group"><div class="overview-chart" data-chart-value="95, 5" data-chart-label="95">95</div></div><p class="overview-chart-description"><b>Satisfaction:</b>95% of our clients come back <br /> to work with us again.</p></div></div>', 'Software Development Projects', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 12:52:48', '2014-01-22 12:52:48', '', 10, '/10-revision-v1.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(648, 1, '2014-01-23 07:58:15', '2014-01-23 07:58:15', '<h4>Why should you choose SETA?</h4><p>Companies are under pressure to lower development costs while maintaining quality. To do more with less, they hire "cheap" offshore developers and quickly become frustrated with the skill gap, lack of IP Protection, language barrier, time zone and cultural issues that plague most offshore relationships. Seta International was founded by two Fortune 100 execs who experienced this frustration on a daily basis and set out to create a better solution.</p><p>Our past experience inspired us to create Setas industry leading Hybrid Onshore-Offshore development model. This hybrid model provides lower total cost while maximizing efficiency and production.</p><p>Seta is a custom software development company headquartered in Southern California with worldwide offices in Ireland, Japan and Vietnam. We leverage our talents in the best-cost locations to fulfill your project requirements. For example, you may find that we utilize talented system architects in Ireland, creative U.S. Graphic Designers, and efficient software developers in Vietnam to deliver a perfect blend of low cost and high quality.</p><p>Our clients typically fall into two categories. One is a fixed project where you tell us what outcome you need and we build it for a fixed cost. An example of this is a standard app development project. A U.S. based Project Manager gathers your requirements. He then directs the design, development, and testing to deliver your product for final approval. Its that simple.</p><p>The second category is our "Dedicated Team" model, also known as "Staff Augmentation". Imagine hand picking a team of talented engineers to augment your current staff, with the flexibility to add or remove resources based on demand. Your local project manager will create a roadmap including specs and resource requirements, meet with Setas global HR department to align the best talent for your needs, and send the candidates to you for final approval. This team acts as an extension of your internal organization. The Project Manager stays with you the entire duration of the project to ensure all expectations are met.</p><p>We at Seta know you need more than "cheap" development costs. You also need quality, efficiency, flexibility, and scalability. We have a 97% project success rate with many returning clients. We always come through for our clients and we will come through for you.</p><table class="program"><tbody><tr><th>Programming Languages (Web)</th><th>Programming Languages (Mobile)</th><th>Database Expertise</th><th>Operating Systems</th></tr><tr><td>C# / ASP.NET <br /> Java (J2ME, J2SE, J2EE) <br /> Rich Media (Adobe Flash, <br /> Action Script, HTML5, CSS3) <br /> Linux/Unix C/C++ <br /> Window C/C++ <br /> Script Languages (PHP, Perl, <br /> Javascript, Python)</td><td>iPhone/iPad <br /> Android <br /> Blackberry <br /> Windows Mobile</td><td>JMS SQL Server <br /> Oracle <br /> MySQL <br /> DB2</td><td>Solaris / HPUX / AIX <br /> Windows <br /> Various versions of Linux</td></tr></tbody></table>', 'The international technology partner you can trust', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-international-technology-partner-you-can-trust-4', '', '', '2014-01-29 01:25:51', '2014-01-29 01:25:51', '', 0, '/?page_id=648', 0, 'page', '', 0),
